citation: Vehicle and Traffic Amendment (Heavy Vehicle Charges) Act 2004 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Vehicle and Traffic Amendment (Heavy Vehicle Charges) Act 2004 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Vehicle and Traffic Amendment (Heavy Vehicle Charges) Act 2004 has been repealed by Schedule 1 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
